We’ve partnered with @KiddsKids since 2006. Over the last 13 years, we’ve provided air travel, hosted an annual telethon to raise support, and planned send-off events. But this year is extra special.
The very first @KiddsKids trip was a bus ride with five families to San Antonio. That was 28 years ago. Today, we’re helping send 39 families all the way to Orlando.
Kidd Kraddick, a morning show host, had a dream to make a difference in the lives of children who were dealing with life-altering or life-threatening conditions.

Today, we are sending children and their families on the trip of a lifetime to the Happiest Place on Earth, in support of an organization we’re proud to partner with: @KiddsKids. Kidd’s Kids all started as an idea, and it began right here at a radio station in Dallas.
